13/DJI-0250-1763020888.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=BQWteI9XuJnR1oTjfTAJiQ\" data-component-back=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2025/11/13/DJI-0242-1763020890.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=JjGmMPk79NeWZP9Ra2b-BA\" data-component-caption=\"&quot;<p class=\\&quot;Normal\\&quot;>Nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed1ng r\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khu v\\u1ef1c th\\u00e1p Tam Th\\u1eafng ch\\u1ea5t cao g\\u1ea7n m\\u1ed9t m\\u00e9t.<\\/p> <p class=\\&quot;Normal\\&quot;>Th\\u00e1p Tam Th\\u1eafng l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh do doanh nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3, thi c\\u00f4ng trong 75 ng\\u00e0y v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 155 t\\u1ef7 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. C\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh g\\u1ed3m 143 tr\\u1ee5 b\\u00eat\\u00f4ng c\\u1ed1t th\\u00e9p cao t\\u1eeb 4,55 \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u01a1n 34 m, m\\u00f4 ph\\u1ecfng ba m\\u0169i thuy\\u1ec1n v\\u01b0\\u01a1n kh\\u01a1i v\\u00e0 g\\u1ee3i l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed ba l\\u00e0ng Th\\u1eafng Nh\\u1ea5t, Th\\u1eafng Nh\\u00ec, Th\\u1eafng Tam.<\\/p>&quot;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2025/11/13/DJI-0250-1763020888.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=BQWteI9XuJnR1oTjfTAJiQ\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"banner-ads width_common mb20\" style=\"transition: all .6s ease-in-out;\">\n  <div class=\"lazier\" id=\"_break_page_1\" data-component-type=\"_break_page_ads\" data-key=\"1\"></div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"section-inner outset-column gallery-detail-photo\" id=\"gallery-34436886\">\n  <div class=\"medium-insert-embeds medium-insert-embeds-gallery medium-insert-embeds-normal medium-insert-embeds-large\">\n   <figure>\n    <div class=\"medium-insert-embed\">\n     <div class=\"width_common gallery_block gallery_block_full gallery_3item\">\n      <div class=\"inner_gallery owl-carousel\">\n       <div class=\"item_gallery\" data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"gallery\" data-component-value1=\"https://i